## Linking Conventions

### Logseq-Style Tags
- **Format:** `[[Entity Name]]`
- **Use for:** People, projects, concepts, tools, locations
- **First mention:** Always tag on first mention
- **Subsequent mentions:** Plain text or tag again if creating different context

### Cross-Document References
- **Format:** `[[work/projects/FILENAME]]` or `[[work/meetings/FILENAME]]`
- **Use relative paths** from workspace root
- **Include section anchors** when referencing specific sections: `[[work/projects/FILE#section]]`

### What to Tag
- ‚úÖ **People:** `[[Fabian Muessig]]`, `[[Olivia Rossetti]]`
- ‚úÖ **Projects:** `[[SE-NTRAL]]`, `[[Mission Control]]`
- ‚úÖ **Concepts:** `[[Solution Integrity]]`, `[[Launch]]`, `[[Handoff]]`
- ‚úÖ **Tools:** `[[SE-Assistant]]`, `[[Salesforce]]`
- ‚úÖ **Locations:** `[[Dublin]]`, `[[EMEA]]`
